## Frontend — Core Web Vitals

The `web-vitals` library (v4+) tracks the five standard performance metrics:
CLS, FCP, INP, LCP, and TTFB.

```typescript
import { reportWebVitals } from '@/lib/profiling';

// Log to console in development
reportWebVitals(console.log);

// Send to analytics endpoint
reportWebVitals((metric) => {
  navigator.sendBeacon('/api/v1/analytics/vitals', JSON.stringify(metric));
});
```

